          "activation_name": "Reveal Demons",
          "critical_failure": "As failure, but with a duration of 10 minutes.",
          "effect": "You brandish *Morning Glow* and focus on its gleaming light, boosting its illumination so that it produces bright light in a 30-foot emanation (and dim light for another 30 feet) for 10 minutes. All creatures in this area that have the demon trait must attempt a DC 31 Reflex save.",
          "failure": "The demon becomes outlined with a shimmering aura of dim light that causes it to become dazzled. If the demon was invisible, it becomes concealed instead. If it was already concealed for any other reason, it is no longer concealed. This light affects the demon for 1 minute.",
          "frequency": "once per hour",
          "links": [
            {
